How to install TkServ
---------------------

(This installation procedure assumes that you have already installed the
irc server.)

1. RTFM (the README).
2. Edit tkconf.h.
3. Type "make install-tkserv" in the appropriate directory.
   (Type "make" for all possible options.)
3. Edit the TkServ configuration file.
4. Start up TkServ.

Good luck, Kasi
